headline: Toll Brothers (TOL) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Toll Brothers (TOL) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 7.67% and 5.31%, respectively, for the quarter ended October 2024. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
